# psi4 filename           number of columns    w_lower_cut                Madm                 t_start    t_end
'PSI4FNAME'         NCOL             OMEGAVAL      ADMMASS    TSTART    TEND

#   ! Note: The parameter w_lower_cut refers to the *orbital* angular velocity in code unit, 
#   !       not the (2,2) mode of GW frequency.
#   ! GW strain with t<t_start and t>t_end will be set to 0
#   !

